    q: "Can you fix a 16-year-old DCS BGA36?",
    a: "Probably yes. Most failures on older DCS units are ceramic radiants, igniter electrodes, and U-burner pinholes, all current parts that fit older models. The grill body and frame are typically still excellent at 16+ years (DCS construction is among the most durable in the premium grill market). We diagnose, quote, and tell you straight if repair makes sense.",
  },
